          <p>World Spine Care vigorously upholds gender equality in all its undertakings as a fundamental principle, and gender equality will be actively pursued through the following mechanisms:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>All World Spine Care clinics will be equally available to all local residents, with no gender bias.</li>
            <li>The training program being designed for front-line health care workers will incorporate gender equality as a foundational principle.</li>
            <li>It is expected that a strong majority of the front-line health care workers trained in the WSC model of care will be women.</li>
